  "description": "<h3><strong>Fresh without experience-Starting basic is $2600-$3000</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Industry: Engineering</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Located at Chai Chee</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Japanese MNC</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Have AWS + Bonus + Yearly increment</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist Supervisor in day-to-day operation lines.</li>\n  <li>Planning &amp; Co-coordinating the workflow on production lines to achieve production targets.</li>\n  <li>Trouble shooting production problems and assist in planning new project work.</li>\n  <li>Groom to be leader</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Engineering</li>\n  <li>No experience / fresh entry welcome to apply</li>\n  <li>Have driving license</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Applications:</strong></p>\n<p>Please submit a copy of your updated CV in MS Word format stating to <strong>emilyfong@atomrecruit.com</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Current Salary</li>\n  <li>Expected Salary</li>\n  <li>Date of Available and Reason for Leaving</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>All applicant will treated private and confidential</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Emily Fong</strong></p>\n<p>Senior Talent Specialist</p>\n<p>Atomrecruit Pte. Ltd. | MOM EA License No.: 15C7443</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Reg No.: R1768368</p>",
